dc_title_s: Messin Nova Territorii Metensis Descriptio; autore Abrahamo Fabert.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. North is oriented to the right of the map. Includes two coat of arms in the upper right and left corners. Similar to the state listed in Van der Krogt's Atlantes Neerlandici but lacks Henricus Hondius' name from the title cartouche. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 47 x 37 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
